{"tid":1419513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請即停止消極、分化、埋怨","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:01:58.000Z","uid":266924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86253f11e05238b737c1e2b5492504ab9d9b0b47","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"事實上係比你地想像中好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一）街坊已經主動出擊<br />\n二）政府一直無力應對<br />\n三）黑警情緒每況愈下<br />\n四）黑惡勢力受人厭惡<br />\n五）流水抗爭戰略出色</span><br />\n大家堅持咁耐，可能會灰心失望<br />\n見到義士被捕心感憂傷<br />\n有人開始疲倦，有人開始低沉<br />\n唔緊要，你地去休息一下，反省自身，審視一下目標方向<br />\n等我地另一班精神既出黎接力發夢<br />\n今次係長期抗爭，事情除左係保護香港司法獨立，仲有係對政制缺憾而行動<br />\n爭取普選，主權在民，抗衡政府，你我有責<br />\n<br />\n大家記住<br />\n提防左膠，勇武非勇武不分化不割蓆<br />\n我相信我地一直行係正確，亦係踏上光輝之路途"},{"pid":"bf441f3617a8de179d412f841dccdf1f78a825f0","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3e3dc0cf1fd72356fa49902caca13bf0b23f283","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7154476a2c4b37abc1275cba1d046fb2f1b0665b","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68b3f83bbfcadafc5c94ba370b515f27e0bd971b","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:42:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ae05efdb62256728d2016ba7a0331fe19c4cf4","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32eace561dae5a0a98eb6362310f17b366d2b25","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a04044e3f8e1fcbc0f6764f4459053b1be221d1","tid":1419513,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:49:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"178e1204465d57a15aa4ffe7f3347af3b339a06b